---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Brendan Bennett">
  <h1>Brendan Bennett</h1>
  <p class="subtitle">Welcome to my corner of the internet.</p>

  <section>
    <h2>About</h2>
    <p>
      I'm a researcher and writer interested in the places where technology,
      science, and human experience intersect. My work spans computational
      methods, data analysis, and the broader questions that emerge when we
      look closely at complex systems.
    </p>
    <p>
      When I'm not buried in code or papers, you'll find me reading widely,
      exploring new ideas, and occasionally writing about things that catch my
      attention. I believe in working openly, thinking carefully, and building
      things that matter.
    </p>
    <p>
      This site is a place for me to share my research, collect my thoughts,
      and keep a record of what I've been working on. Feel free to look around.
    </p>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  .subtitle {
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  section {
    margin-top: 1rem;
  }
</style>
